DRY (Don't repeat yoursel)

Parenthesized variable declarations 'var'

```go
var (
	a int
	b string
	c bool
)
```

Why not allow a parenthesized method declarations `func Receiver`?

```go
func (*r foo) (
  Foo() int {
    return r.foo
  }

  Baz() string {
    return r.baz
  }

  Bar() bool {
    return r.bar
  }
}
```
